<h2 id="future-plans">Future plans</h2>

<p>Next steps include experimenting with Phantom auto-scaling service <a class="citation" href="#KeaheyEtAl2012">(Keahey et al. 2012)</a> in the Chameleon cloud to elastically provision resources for our use case application.</p>

